it&amp;section=3D1">edit</A>]</SPAN>=20
<SPAN id=3DThe_SHA-1_hash_function class=3Dmw-headline>The SHA-1 hash=20
function</SPAN></H2>
<DIV class=3D"thumb tright">
<DIV style=3D"WIDTH: 302px" class=3Dthumbinner><A class=3Dimage=20
href=3D"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:SHA-1.svg"><IMG =
