.svg.png 2x"></A>=20

<DIV class=3Dthumbcaption>
<DIV class=3Dmagnify><A class=3Dinternal title=3DEnlarge=20
href=3D"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:SHA-1.svg"><IMG alt=3D""=20
