width=3D15 height=3D11></A></DIV>One iteration within the SHA-1 =
compression=20
function:<BR>A, B, C, D and E are 32-bit <A class=3Dmw-redirect=20
title=3D"Word (data type)"=20
href=3D"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_(data_type)">words</A> of the=20
state;<BR><I>F</I> is a nonlinear function that varies;<BR><A =
class=3Dimage=20
title=3D"left shift" =
href=3D"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Lll.png"><IMG=20
alt=3D"left shift"=20
src=3D"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e1/Lll.png" =
width=3D19=20
height=3D10></A><SUB><I>n</I></SUB> denotes a left bit rotation by =
